1
00:00:00,767 --> 00:00:01,668
( Shaiapouf imitating komugi )
Hello?

2
00:00:01,702 --> 00:00:03,170
Sir pitou?

3
00:00:03,971 --> 00:00:05,973
This is komugi.

4
00:00:06,039 --> 00:00:09,709
I’m fine, so please
don’t worry about me.

5
00:00:09,776 --> 00:00:11,344
I’ll be all right.

6
00:00:14,748 --> 00:00:16,183
Neferpitou: I understand.

7
00:00:17,284 --> 00:00:19,119
( Shaiapouf laughs )

8
00:00:19,186 --> 00:00:23,323
And now pitou
is also under my spell.

9
00:00:23,390 --> 00:00:25,792
My lie is like a magic trick

10
00:00:25,859 --> 00:00:28,895
that will release him
from the curse of that girl.

11
00:00:30,931 --> 00:00:32,132
Neferpitou: Gon...

12
00:00:32,199 --> 00:00:35,169
You respected my wishes
and waited for me...

13
00:00:36,970 --> 00:00:40,273
So I feel like I should
at least be honest with you.

14
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:41,308
I owe you that.

15
00:00:45,913 --> 00:00:47,014
This man...

16
00:00:48,215 --> 00:00:50,217
Is...

17
00:00:50,284 --> 00:00:52,253
Already dead.

18
00:00:52,319 --> 00:00:54,855
( Gon gasps )

19
00:00:54,922 --> 00:00:56,857
( Breeze blowing )

20
00:01:05,165 --> 00:01:07,100
( Thud echoing )

21
00:01:09,269 --> 00:01:11,204
♪

22
00:01:14,107 --> 00:01:17,978
Neferpitou: His soul isn’t here,
not anymore,

23
00:01:18,045 --> 00:01:19,847
and I can’t bring him back.

24
00:01:19,913 --> 00:01:21,381
Your friend is gone.

25
00:01:30,357 --> 00:01:32,226
I’m sorry.

26
00:01:32,292 --> 00:01:34,227
( Gon weeping )

27
00:01:39,199 --> 00:01:40,233
Wait.

28
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:43,436
Why are you healing
your own arm?

29
00:01:43,504 --> 00:01:45,940
That doesn’t make any sense.

30
00:01:46,006 --> 00:01:48,208
Turn kite back to normal.

31
00:01:51,311 --> 00:01:56,016
Please, you can do that
after you finish healing kite.

32
00:01:56,083 --> 00:01:57,952
Please just do it, okay?

33
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,454
♪

34
00:02:00,521 --> 00:02:02,390
( Singing in Japanese )

35
00:02:44,097 --> 00:02:46,032
♪

36
00:02:53,473 --> 00:02:55,041
( Wings fluttering )

37
00:02:55,108 --> 00:02:57,444
Shaiapouf: The tables
have been turned.

38
00:02:57,511 --> 00:02:59,813
( Palm and killua gasp )

39
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:01,882
Shaiapouf: Pitou believes
we have been successful

40
00:03:01,949 --> 00:03:04,785
in our attempt
to recover komugi.

41
00:03:04,852 --> 00:03:06,320
From the look of it,

42
00:03:06,386 --> 00:03:09,789
gon is almost certainly going
to be killed before too long.

43
00:03:09,857 --> 00:03:15,796
You stand no chance of stopping
pitou yourselves, but I can.

44
00:03:15,863 --> 00:03:17,998
And if you’ll
just hand the girl over,

45
00:03:18,065 --> 00:03:20,167
i’ll be glad
to stop pitou for you.

46
00:03:25,873 --> 00:03:27,208
( Gasps )

47
00:03:27,274 --> 00:03:29,743
Killua: You’d better
start running,

48
00:03:29,810 --> 00:03:31,178
you son of a bitch.

49
00:03:31,245 --> 00:03:33,681
♪

50
00:03:33,747 --> 00:03:36,116
Palm: You can
leave her to my care.

51
00:03:36,183 --> 00:03:41,822
I swear upon these eyes that I
will never let them have her.

52
00:03:41,889 --> 00:03:45,025
Killua: Yeah. I trust you.

53
00:03:45,092 --> 00:03:46,393
Speed of lightning!

54
00:03:49,296 --> 00:03:52,800
Gon, just hang on
until I get there.

55
00:04:08,248 --> 00:04:10,183
( Gon crying )

56
00:04:15,455 --> 00:04:17,390
( Surgical tools clattering )

57
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:55,195
( Exoskeleton crackling )

58
00:05:05,205 --> 00:05:06,740
Neferpitou: Gon...

59
00:05:08,141 --> 00:05:11,645
I’m sorry, but i’m afraid...

60
00:05:12,846 --> 00:05:14,881
I have to kill you now...

61
00:05:17,851 --> 00:05:20,187
For the sake of the king.

62
00:05:20,254 --> 00:05:22,957
♪

63
00:05:23,023 --> 00:05:24,992
( Chorus vocalizing )

64
00:05:31,365 --> 00:05:34,401
Gon: You have to kill me?

65
00:05:34,468 --> 00:05:37,905
So you’re not gonna heal him?

66
00:05:41,909 --> 00:05:45,346
You aren’t gonna heal kite?

67
00:05:45,412 --> 00:05:48,749
You’re just leaving him there?

68
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,955
( Chorus continues )

69
00:06:02,696 --> 00:06:04,264
You’re such a liar.

70
00:06:14,975 --> 00:06:16,877
( Neferpitou gasps )

71
00:06:27,387 --> 00:06:29,322
♪

72
00:06:31,391 --> 00:06:33,326
( Breeze blowing )

73
00:06:41,835 --> 00:06:43,770
( Chorus continues )

74
00:06:57,251 --> 00:06:58,319
( Lamp shatters )

75
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,267
What...

76
00:07:15,235 --> 00:07:17,871
What is this?

77
00:07:23,810 --> 00:07:25,278
( Chorus continues )

78
00:07:28,782 --> 00:07:30,384
Gon: Enough.

79
00:07:34,188 --> 00:07:36,824
I don’t care
what happens to me now.

80
00:07:36,890 --> 00:07:39,226
♪

81
00:08:12,326 --> 00:08:14,195
I need...

82
00:08:14,261 --> 00:08:17,364
All the power i’ll ever have.

83
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:27,040
Neferpitou: I knew it.
I was right about him.

84
00:08:28,375 --> 00:08:30,344
As I feared,

85
00:08:30,410 --> 00:08:33,847
his fangs might even
sink into the king.

86
00:08:38,118 --> 00:08:40,354
Gon: I’m gonna kill you.

87
00:08:44,725 --> 00:08:46,827
Pitou!

88
00:08:50,297 --> 00:08:52,232
♪

89
00:08:58,305 --> 00:08:59,406
( Neferpitou gasps )

90
00:08:59,473 --> 00:09:01,041
Terpsichora.

91
00:09:04,144 --> 00:09:07,047
Dance beyond my limit!

92
00:09:15,255 --> 00:09:18,792
I have to stop him here and now.

93
00:09:18,859 --> 00:09:20,260
( Gasps )

94
00:09:26,767 --> 00:09:29,069
( Gasps )

95
00:09:37,811 --> 00:09:39,279
It can’t be.

96
00:09:40,981 --> 00:09:43,083
Is he heading for the king?

97
00:10:10,177 --> 00:10:12,212
Gon: Come with me.

98
00:10:13,981 --> 00:10:17,718
I don’t want
to destroy the hideout.

99
00:10:28,795 --> 00:10:30,330
Come this way.

100
00:10:33,767 --> 00:10:35,435
Just follow me.

101
00:10:43,043 --> 00:10:44,978
♪

102
00:11:30,557 --> 00:11:33,827
Neferpitou: I don’t know
how he did it,

103
00:11:33,894 --> 00:11:36,663
but he’s forced
his body to mature

104
00:11:37,965 --> 00:11:41,268
to an age
where he can defeat me.

105
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:48,675
( Chorus vocalizing )

106
00:11:56,383 --> 00:11:58,685
( Exoskeleton crackling )

107
00:12:07,327 --> 00:12:09,229
♪

108
00:12:21,942 --> 00:12:23,844
( Gasps )

109
00:12:32,953 --> 00:12:34,455
( Groans )

110
00:12:44,565 --> 00:12:46,667
Gon: Show me...

111
00:12:52,539 --> 00:12:53,573
Rock.

112
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:02,249
♪

113
00:13:16,330 --> 00:13:18,632
( Neferpitou groaning )

114
00:13:24,705 --> 00:13:27,641
Gon: Jan Ken...

115
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:31,678
Rock.

116
00:13:31,745 --> 00:13:33,247
( Neferpitou gasps )

117
00:13:48,829 --> 00:13:51,765
Narrator: At the edge
of fading consciousness,

118
00:13:51,832 --> 00:13:53,901
pitou was relieved.

119
00:13:55,569 --> 00:13:57,271
Neferpitou: Thank goodness.

120
00:14:02,442 --> 00:14:06,413
There’s only one way he could
have achieved this power,

121
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:08,849
by compressing his own life.

122
00:14:08,916 --> 00:14:13,421
He was prepared
to burn himself out completely

123
00:14:13,487 --> 00:14:16,156
and never be able
to use nen again.

124
00:14:16,223 --> 00:14:19,460
That was the resolve
required to do this.

125
00:14:19,526 --> 00:14:21,228
( Birds squawking )

126
00:14:26,733 --> 00:14:30,203
This boy was born
with an incredible gift,

127
00:14:30,270 --> 00:14:34,341
but, even so,
he didn’t hesitate.

128
00:14:34,408 --> 00:14:38,279
He was willing
to throw that gift away.

129
00:14:38,345 --> 00:14:39,613
( Footsteps pounding )

130
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:41,615
( Chorus vocalizing )

131
00:14:46,420 --> 00:14:52,660
Thank goodness
I was the one to die.

132
00:14:58,932 --> 00:15:01,868
( Brush rustles )

133
00:15:04,571 --> 00:15:06,506
Narrator:
Using speed of lightning

134
00:15:06,573 --> 00:15:08,275
to race to gon’s location,

135
00:15:08,342 --> 00:15:10,845
killua arrived
just in time to hear...

136
00:15:10,911 --> 00:15:12,846
( Whoosh )

137
00:15:12,913 --> 00:15:13,847
( Killua gasps )

138
00:15:13,914 --> 00:15:15,282
( Boom )

139
00:15:16,517 --> 00:15:18,652
( Whoosh )

140
00:15:18,719 --> 00:15:20,821
( Boom )

141
00:15:20,888 --> 00:15:23,491
( Whoosh )

142
00:15:23,557 --> 00:15:24,658
( Boom )

143
00:15:24,725 --> 00:15:27,628
Killua: Whoa. Who is that?

144
00:15:27,694 --> 00:15:29,863
( Whoosh )

145
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:31,432
( Boom )

146
00:15:32,566 --> 00:15:33,867
Gon.

147
00:15:33,934 --> 00:15:35,536
( Whoosh )

148
00:15:35,602 --> 00:15:38,271
Narrator: And that
was when he saw...

149
00:15:38,338 --> 00:15:42,175
( Whoosh )

150
00:15:42,242 --> 00:15:43,910
( Boom )

151
00:15:45,312 --> 00:15:46,647
( Whoosh )

152
00:15:46,713 --> 00:15:50,517
An unfamiliar silhouette,
one he had never before,

153
00:15:50,584 --> 00:15:54,688
and a fist stained with blood
from countless blows.

154
00:15:54,755 --> 00:15:57,491
That fist smashed pitou’s head
to a pulp,

155
00:15:57,558 --> 00:15:59,894
though pitou lay limp as a rag.

156
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:03,397
Gon: Jan Ken...

157
00:16:04,798 --> 00:16:07,601
( Boom )

158
00:16:09,369 --> 00:16:13,540
Narrator: Gon reared back
for the final shattering blow.

159
00:16:26,253 --> 00:16:27,387
Gon: Kite...

160
00:16:29,323 --> 00:16:31,525
I made sure to finish it,

161
00:16:31,592 --> 00:16:33,894
just like you taught me.

162
00:16:37,397 --> 00:16:38,865
So...

163
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:50,544
Killua: Gon, is that you?

164
00:16:56,450 --> 00:16:58,652
Gon: Hi, killua.

165
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:02,389
Narrator: Having seen
gon’s appearance,

166
00:17:02,456 --> 00:17:05,426
killua immediately
thought of biscuit.

167
00:17:05,492 --> 00:17:09,629
However, he realized
the difference in an instant.

168
00:17:09,696 --> 00:17:12,465
Killua:
Bisky’s appearance changed,

169
00:17:12,533 --> 00:17:15,669
but there wasn’t a massive
increase in her internal aura,

170
00:17:15,736 --> 00:17:18,672
and, in bisky’s case,
she wasn’t aging herself.

171
00:17:18,739 --> 00:17:22,142
All she was doing was
reverting to her original form.

172
00:17:22,209 --> 00:17:24,745
But gon’s done
the complete opposite.

173
00:17:24,811 --> 00:17:26,746
♪

174
00:17:26,813 --> 00:17:28,581
How many years?

175
00:17:28,649 --> 00:17:32,186
More than ten? Decades?

176
00:17:32,252 --> 00:17:33,520
This is what he would look like

177
00:17:33,587 --> 00:17:36,390
after years and years
of training.

178
00:17:39,827 --> 00:17:43,531
What price did he have to pay
to obtain this much aura?

179
00:17:46,233 --> 00:17:47,534
( Gasps )

180
00:18:18,198 --> 00:18:19,132
( Slice )

181
00:18:58,505 --> 00:19:02,609
Narrator: Pitou’s terpsichora,
with aura amplified by death,

182
00:19:02,676 --> 00:19:05,712
became an undead puppet
for the king.

183
00:19:05,779 --> 00:19:10,684
It had but a single purpose,
to attack and kill gon.

184
00:19:10,751 --> 00:19:14,488
It crouched and waited
for the right moment.

185
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:20,160
And then,
in that fraction of a second,

186
00:19:20,227 --> 00:19:21,829
shorter than
the blink of an eye,

187
00:19:21,895 --> 00:19:25,432
killua swore he heard gon speak.

188
00:19:25,499 --> 00:19:27,901
Gon: It’s okay. I’m fine.

189
00:19:31,205 --> 00:19:34,775
It doesn’t hurt.
I’m not bluffing.

190
00:19:37,244 --> 00:19:40,314
I’m actually kind of happy.

191
00:19:43,217 --> 00:19:50,257
Finally I can be
just like kite was in the end.

192
00:19:52,426 --> 00:19:53,360
Killua: Gon.

193
00:19:57,331 --> 00:19:59,400
Gon: I feel...

194
00:19:59,466 --> 00:20:01,401
A little better now.

195
00:20:08,442 --> 00:20:11,779
( Yells )

196
00:20:17,251 --> 00:20:19,553
You can have my right arm.

197
00:20:20,654 --> 00:20:21,855
All right, now.

198
00:20:21,922 --> 00:20:23,957
Show me rock.

199
00:20:29,263 --> 00:20:30,831
( Killua gasps ) Gon, no!

200
00:20:31,932 --> 00:20:35,369
Gon: Now you can sleep.

201
00:20:38,906 --> 00:20:41,876
Killua: Gon, stop it, please.

202
00:20:41,942 --> 00:20:43,811
Don’t use any more power.

203
00:20:43,877 --> 00:20:46,380
How much will you have to pay?

204
00:20:46,446 --> 00:20:47,814
It’s too much.

205
00:20:47,881 --> 00:20:49,383
Gon: Jan...

206
00:20:51,485 --> 00:20:53,220
Ken...

207
00:20:57,891 --> 00:21:00,327
Killua: Gon!

208
00:21:12,406 --> 00:21:14,341
♪

209
00:21:25,619 --> 00:21:27,454
( Singing in Japanese )

